{"tid":1747281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽]聽日唔含淚，以後就含撚啦","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:19:26.000Z","uid":78790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f818710a1dfd3ad3734395bc31f3e068887f3e","tid":1747281,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n其實大家搞清楚未<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家<span style=\"color: red;\">首要敵人</span>係建制<br />\n係民建聯<br />\n係紅底偽獨立<br />\n<br />\n而家<span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆</span>已經唔係淨係話比自己人聽<br />\n要<span style=\"color: red;\">講埋比國際社會聽呀</span><br />\n<br />\n我撚唔知你杯葛緊個選舉制度咩<br />\n但一日個投票制度仲係度<br />\n條數就一日有人用黎reference反映民意<br />\n而家拖撚返泛民啲屎出黎講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係咪想唔夠人投泛民就變建制贏！？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你聽日仲係堅持唔含淚<br />\n咁你就等含撚啦<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"568c6e9f3d77decdb3a1035be51c6fe921905d99","tid":1747281,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a935ccdaa54663cbf8b6744ab3a9db0085644bdb","tid":1747281,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d2235303a3fc9497ed1aa63bff7364fdc5e2398","tid":1747281,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:04:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6934f86731070ec80a8ef179e9e4b2904d3391df","tid":1747281,"uid":251265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:04:06.000Z","msg":"企圖抹黑民主派，呼籲手足投白票一律視為共諜"},{"pid":"567ae0ac7cbfad17e5e451c7ed7ea75d4e91b5b3","tid":1747281,"uid":325884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"票投民賤聯，香港玩撚完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d10a2200795c7a58a82608aba696e4728d7778a","tid":1747281,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14a5980a75255bee2b58d511cd12